611
00:29:17,244 --> 00:29:19,565
If Chen Luzhou

612
00:29:20,725 --> 00:29:22,244
cheats on Zhi,

613
00:29:24,925 --> 00:29:25,685
I will...

614
00:29:28,965 --> 00:29:29,765
