It's been several days.

796
00:37:05,525 --> 00:37:06,605
Yet very few customers.

797
00:37:07,284 --> 00:37:09,164
Can we make money this way?

798
00:37:09,685 --> 00:37:10,485
I don't know.

799
00:37:10,565 --> 00:37:12,605
